&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Coordinate smooth handoffs to onboarding teams and escalate non-standard scenarios as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
